      "content": "that makes sense. it's good to know there's a formal checklist. i guess i'm just a bit nervous about the whole 'holding' aspect though. it feels like there's a lot of risk when a big chunk of money is just sitting there in someone else's hands waiting for things to clear. are there any specific things i should look out for to make sure it's being handled right?",
